-- Chelsea Defeats Liverpool 2-1 in English F.A. Cup Soccer Final
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-05-05T18:09:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-05/chelsea-defeats-liverpool-2-1-in-english-f-a-cup-soccer-final.html
Chelsea defeated Liverpool 2-1 in the
English F.A. Cup soccer final at Wembley Stadium in  London .  Ramires and Didier Drogba scored as Chelsea won its fourth
F.A. Cup title in six seasons and seventh overall. Andy Carroll
scored for Liverpool, which was seeking its eighth F.A. Cup.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  